Ur own baerteder is great.  Good drinks and lots but i do not stop.  At some point i start thinking and i thought i was over thinking.

WOW it has been a long time since i poisted on this place.

I have been dealt the worst set of cards ever.
Life is just kicking me and kicking me.
And when I think i am ok it finds a new way to kick me.
I am never going to get back in the game.
Its my last hand and all my chips are are on the table and I have nothing in my hand.
Why would I think I could ever be dealt anything to change this.

All I get is a few days of the smallest amount of good and then it is all over and I am worse then when I went into it.  I just finished 14 or so shows of Beauty and the Beast and they went great.  They made me feel so good.  Everyone in the cast and crew was amazing.  But now it is over and I have to go back to my real life and my problems.
When I think something has changed or I got someting worked out I find out I was wrong.  It takes so long to figure out a solution that works for me and it gets killed in 2o seconds.

I just need to give up caring about my life.  If I do not excpect anything from myself or anyone else "Ill escape now from this world from the world of..."

I need to get away form it all.  If I deal with my problems it hurts and if i run away from them it hurts even more.  But i can not deal with anymore pain.
I know something is wrong when drinking does not help anymore.
I cannot sleep good.
I think I am going to go get a drink now.
good bye

I have lost all feeling.
I am just a empty shell.
I stab yet i do not feel.
I cannot do this much longer.
Something needs to happen.

Drinking fixes so many problems.
It makes me feel nice and happy most of the time.
And not much can get to me.
But then you have the other times that it just reminds me more of my problems.
Tonight I was happy.

The big problem with drinking is that when the buz is all over your problems hit you even harder.
It is not that I drank much tonight it is more that i drank it quick so my buz is done now and i need to shut off my brain.
Wish i could just do a "shutdown -p now" to my brain.
I guess the Eagles losing did not help.

I need to find my life again.
I can never be the same again but not sure if I would want to.
Damn it I wish i would get an interview.

I need to go sleep or drink more not sure what one but in any case I know i will not be able to type then.
Night from my Buz.

Tonight the 6 of us went to see complete works in princeton.
IT was GREAT.
I would go back to see it again if i had time.
I got to talk to there lighting guy and ask him some questions that i did not want to ask after the show when the cast and all was taking questions from the audience.
I was not going to go find him and ask so KB went and asked for me ;-)
Twas funny.
Glad she did the guy was cool and a CS major.
But if u get techies talking it could be hrs we would talk for.
We all had a good time.
I think we needed it.
I have 2 parties to go to this weekend with them.
Should be good but interesting :-d

Even with it being a good day and all I feel like shit.
Not my body but my spirit and soul and brain.
I am going to lose it.
I feel like such an ass.  I do not know what to do. Make it all END.
I do not even know what I want anymore.
It hurts so much but i cannot feel any different.
I can never bring myself to feel any different.
I just wish i knew why i feel like this.

Hell sounds like a good thing right now to how I am feeling.
But I have to get to bed.
Need to be up early cause I have so much shit to do at home.
And I need to go pick up Jeep from the dealer cause I think we finally figured out what was wrong with it.
And I have to do all this before i go pick up the gang to go to the party.

*HUG*
~Peter

WOW it has been a long time since I posted to LJ.
Not dead yet try again later.
I have been so busy that I have not had time too.
And just have not been in the mood to post.
Not in the mood to do a lot of things now.

Today I had my last class at widener :-)
I have all my classes done now to get my BS.
All this bull shit for a piece of paper.
I did not think I was going to make it.
I was just about to kill my Profs for my one class.
But I made it and it all good now.
It has been one hell of 6 weeks for summer school.
They cannot make 15 weeks of work into 6 without not doing some stuff.
But u cannot tell the Profs that.

Other then school it has been a great few weeks.
Last Fri I went with KB to see My Fair Lady in Princeton.
It was one of the best shows I have EVER seen.
They did such a good job I wish I could go again.
But the show also made me think and that is never good.
I did cry during it too.
I always cry during one of the songs but a few others made me cry.
After that I got to go to the beach for the weekend and that was great weather.
I did not want to leave other then it was Fathers day and I had to go home.

This week is going to be a party week ;-)
Fri. I am going to see Complete Works in Princeton.
Have a party this weekend to go to.
And then I want to party for the rest of the week.
Along with sleep and just LOTS OF FUN.
I AM FREE FROM WIDENER.

But now that I am done I have time to think.
This cannot be good cause I still do not know how to feel.
Everything still does not feel right.
I thought it was cause of school but i still do not feel good.
I feel better but not like i should
Sometimes you can't express how you feel cause words just can't explain it.
It pains me to think about it but I have no idea what I am going to do.
I am torn and there is nothing that I can do to fix it.
In my PSY class we were talking about stress and did a stress test.
The rest of the class was around 150 - 200 but my stress level is 600.
I know, not like I was surprised but that just adds to the fact that I need to figure this 

stuff out or I will burst.  And burst icky no burst.
We are talking about lots of the stress and stuff 
but not something I cannot talk about because then the feeling comes back to the surface.
I do not show my feelings and I know it not good to hold them in but I have so much held 

inside that if I let it all out it will kill me or greatly hurt others I care about.
I care too much to just let it all go.
I do not know if I can take it anymore. grrrrr
I feel like I am always wrong and cannot come up with the right answers.
For once I wish something could just go right.

I need to look on the better side of things.
I WILL HAVE A GOOD WEEKEND ;-)
I am ok I just had to get some stuff out

Night
Love
*Hug*
~Peter

Kill me now.
I cannot take it anymore.
Just make it all go away.

The last 2 weeks have been hell.
I just do not know what is right anymore.
I just do not know what to do.

The theatre is driving me nuts.
It is going to kill me.
I cannot work like this anymore.
I am spending over 9 hrs a day in the theater.
I would be ok but I have class and HW to.
I come back from the theatre at 11pm and I cannot move it hurts so much.
I got the best damn stair master in the theater (aka 14' ladder).
And then I get to do all my HW and somehow get up for class in the AM.
I know I am overdoing it but there is nothing I can do about.
I have to work this hard to get it all done.
We open in a week and I will be home for 3 of those days.
Widener is fucking us over by not doing stuff until the last min.

This is my last show at Widener and I want it to be great but the way it is going it will not be.
It all depends on how much I get done and I cannot deal with that pressure right now.
I am not going to be able to take it if the show is not good as the other shows I have done.
That is just not an option for me.
I have enough shit going on that I do not need this.

Sorry about this post but I just needed to vent.
I am about to snap.
I almost went off at the cast tonight and it would have been for no reason.
I cannot take it.

I am so tired tonight I hope I can sleep.
Good night
Sorry

~Peter
